1137 def experimental_thread_pool_handle(num_threads, display_name, max_intra_op_parallelism=1, container="", shared_name="", name=None):
1138   r"""Creates a dataset that uses a custom thread pool to compute `input_dataset`.
1139 
1140   Args:
1141     num_threads: An `int`. The number of threads in the thread pool.
1142     display_name: A `string`.
1143       A human-readable name for the threads that may be visible in some
1144       visualizations.
1145       threadpool.
1146     max_intra_op_parallelism: An optional `int`. Defaults to `1`.
1147       The maximum degree of parallelism to use within operations that execute on this
1148       threadpool.
1149     container: An optional `string`. Defaults to `""`.
1150     shared_name: An optional `string`. Defaults to `""`.
1151     name: A name for the operation (optional).
1152 
1153   Returns:
1154     A `Tensor` of type `resource`.
1155   """
1156   _ctx = _context._context
1157   if _ctx is None or not _ctx._eager_context.is_eager:
1158     num_threads = _execute.make_int(num_threads, "num_threads")
1159     display_name = _execute.make_str(display_name, "display_name")
1160     if max_intra_op_parallelism is None:
1161       max_intra_op_parallelism = 1
1162     max_intra_op_parallelism = _execute.make_int(max_intra_op_parallelism, "max_intra_op_parallelism")
1163     if container is None:
1164       container = ""
1165     container = _execute.make_str(container, "container")
1166     if shared_name is None:
1167       shared_name = ""
1168     shared_name = _execute.make_str(shared_name, "shared_name")
1169     _, _, _op = _op_def_lib._apply_op_helper(
1170         "ExperimentalThreadPoolHandle", num_threads=num_threads,
1171         display_name=display_name,
1172         max_intra_op_parallelism=max_intra_op_parallelism,
1173         container=container, shared_name=shared_name, name=name)
1174     _result = _op.outputs[:]
1175     _inputs_flat = _op.inputs
1176     _attrs = ("num_threads", _op.get_attr("num_threads"),
1177               "max_intra_op_parallelism",
1178               _op.get_attr("max_intra_op_parallelism"), "display_name",
1179               _op.get_attr("display_name"), "container",
1180               _op.get_attr("container"), "shared_name",
1181               _op.get_attr("shared_name"))
1182     _execute.record_gradient(
1183       "ExperimentalThreadPoolHandle", _inputs_flat, _attrs, _result, name)
1184     _result, = _result
1185     return _result

1187   else:
1188     try:
1189       _result = _pywrap_tensorflow.TFE_Py_FastPathExecute(
1190         _ctx._context_handle, _ctx._eager_context.device_name,
1191         "ExperimentalThreadPoolHandle", name, _ctx._post_execution_callbacks,
1192         "num_threads", num_threads, "max_intra_op_parallelism",

1195       return _result
1196     except _core._FallbackException:
1197       return experimental_thread_pool_handle_eager_fallback(
1198           num_threads=num_threads,
1199           max_intra_op_parallelism=max_intra_op_parallelism,
1200           display_name=display_name, container=container,
1201           shared_name=shared_name, name=name, ctx=_ctx)
1202     except _core._NotOkStatusException as e:
1203       if name is not None:
